#           Run                                                                                 #
#           $ <dir-path to tzim.py>/tzim.py                                                     #
#           follow instructions. When conversed, open zim and add repository (i.e. target dir)  #
#                                                                                               #
#           Please send notes that failed to convert to bengt at blafs com.                     #
